title: Useful and fun
comment: Makes it easy to meet up with someone without a lot of planning and its fun to be able to check  where they're at.

title: Great app
comment: Lots of fun! Shows you where you've been and how long you've been there. I used it on my old Android 2.2 phone and it worked as seamlessly as it does on my new Nexus 4!
Force closes everytime its opened. Motorola Droid.
